## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

| Issue | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| **MCP server not responding** | Server crashed or not started | Restart your IDE or run `harness doctor` to verify |
| **`verify_run` fails on lint** | Linting changed files only, but files outside scope | Check `verify.yaml` → set `changed_only: false` for full lint |
| **`skill_load` returns empty** | Skill name typo or doesn't exist | Run `harness skills --list` to see available skills |
| **`scope_check` blocks my edit** | File outside task scope | Review `.harness/scope.yaml` or update task scope |
| **Tests timeout** | Slow tests or network dependency | Check `verify.yaml` → increase `timeout` per step |
| **Session not found error** | Session expired or ID wrong | Run `harness status` to get active session ID |

### Debug Commands

```bash
harness doctor                    # Check system health
harness status --repo .           # Get active session + pending tasks
harness verify --repo .           # Run verification manually
harness skills --list             # List all available skills

# Cross-platform file reading (works on Windows + Unix):
# Windows PowerShell: Get-Content .harness\handoff_last.json
# Unix/Mac: cat .harness/handoff_last.json
# Or use: harness status --repo . (shows handoff info)
```

